tcollector is a framework to collect data points and store them in OpenTSDB.
It allows you to write simple collectors that it'll run and monitor.  It also
handles the communication with the TSDs.

For more info, see

http://www.opentsdb.net/tcollector.html


tcollector.net
--------------

The tcollector.net directory contains a C# plugin framework for OpenTSDB data collection. 
This should make it easier to collect metrics from Windows machines.

It requires the .Net 4.0 framework.
Plugin framework is based on the Managed Extensibility Framework (MEF)
